This isn't just a block of 4 fully refurbished apartments - it's a cash-flowing asset and a development opportunity in one. Located in a high-demand rental area of Hull, just a short walk from the University, all four apartments are fully let until August 2026 on 52-week contracts, with a mix of student and working professional tenants. You're buying into a proven rental performer with hands-off management in place - no voids, no refurb, no hassle. Just solid income from day one. But here's the bonus. To the rear of the site is development land with lapsed planning for 4 additional 2-bed apartments. The design was conservation-friendly, flood-resilient, and previously approved - giving you the chance to double the unit count and seriously increase your GDV and rental income. The projected rental income from the existing flats and new flats once built is £125,000 / year.
